*sigh* <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umdarkelf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mdar kelf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/14/01 11:24:41 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Grabs ankles and holds tightly..</span><hr size=1> verant almost always screws the younger wizards over,  wish they would either give us something worth waiting for, or something that would help us out at the lower lvls. i mean, i could blast every thing till im OOM and almost dead, i could try to show a group that i can save em if need be, i could sacrafice my self to save the healer, but unless those few that see me in action tell my entire server, it wont help me get a group, and wont help other wizards get a group, wish verant would  do something that would make people say, &quot;hey, we have an extra spot open, lets grab that wizard then we could pull almost non stop!&quot;<br>
but no, looks like only raiding wizards will get the good stuff while we wizards that try to get that high must strugal most of the time.....<br>
<br>
oh well, i hear groups in  OT are always in need of extras, maybe ill get picked there.<br>
